### Time Account Management API Tests

# 1. Get API Info
GET http://localhost:3000/

###

# 2. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

# 3. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpassword"
}

###

# 4. Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser", 
  "password": "testpassword"
}

###

# 5. Create Time Account (replace TOKEN_HERE with actual token from login)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/timeaccounts/time-accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
x-password: your_app_password

{
  "userId": 1,
  "hours": 8.5
}

###

# 6. Get all Time Accounts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/timeaccounts/time-accounts
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
x-password: your_app_password

###

# 7. Get Admin Requests
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/requests
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
x-password: your_app_password

###

# 8. Approve a request (replace 1 with actual request ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/approve/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
x-password: your_app_password

###

# 9. Reject a request (replace 1 with actual request ID)  
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/reject/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
x-password: your_app_password